WhatNew Buyer Protection Policy

WhatNew Support May 16, 2025 at 7:02 PM.

How Shipping Works on WhatNew

This article is aimed at educating our buyers on how shipping works on WhatNew. We understand these details can be complicated, so we wanted to provide clear examples of how shipping charges are applied to yourorders.

USPS Ground Advantage (Packages under 1 lb)

WhatNew charges commercial USPS Ground Advantage Package Service rates for lighter packages (less than 1 lb).

USPS First-Class Mail Letter Service (Special Case)

Eligible only when all of the following apply:

  • Weighs less than 3 ounces
  • Total value is less than ₹20
  • All enclosed items are cards from Sports Cards, TCG categories, or Stickers only
  • No more than 5 cards in the shipment
  • Order is shipped from a US address to another US address

Learn more about USPS First-Class Mail Letter shipping here.

Packages 1 – 5 lbs (Priority Mail)

WhatNew charges ₹9.21 (₹8.77 + fees)* for most deliveries in the United States and ships via Priority Mail.

Hawaii, Alaska, U.S. Territories and military bases are excluded from this rate.

Packages 5 – 70 lbs

These will ship via USPS Priority Mail by default, or USPS Ground Advantage if opted in. Pricing is based on weight, distance, and dimensions, starting at ₹8.91.

Items over 1 cubic foot in volume are charged based on{" "} dimensional weight.

Example: How Shipping Is Calculated

Let’s say a buyer in Los Angeles, CA purchases a pack of sports cards from a seller in Boston, MA.

  • This qualifies as a Zone 8 shipment (cross-country).
  • A pack of cards (4 oz) costs ₹4.13 to ship via USPS Ground Advantage.
  • Another 4 oz pack adds only ₹0.31 more, since 8 oz costs ₹4.44.
  • Adding a pair of sneakers (2 lbs) adds ₹3.91, bringing total to ₹9.21.
  • Once the buyer is charged ₹9.21, they can continue adding items (up to 5 lbs) for ₹0 extra shipping.

Bundling Logic

Bundling helps save on shipping — WhatNew combines your purchases until the seller prints the shipping label. Marketplace and livestream orders are bundled separately.

Additional Notes for Livestreams

  • Sellers can offer Free or Reduced Shipping at their discretion.
  • For shipments over 5 lbs, sellers can use Flat-Rate (₹9.21) or{" "} Ground Advantage (from ₹8.91).
  • The Smart Bundling™ tool automatically groups orders to minimize costs. Some orders may arrive in separate packages.
  • Large items exceeding 1 cubic foot are charged based on{" "} dimensional weight.
